This CSS file styles the ToDoList app:

- **Body:** Sets a gradient background and default font.
- **Container:** Centers the app, adds padding, and styles the background with a shadow.
- **Header:** Aligns the logo and title, and styles the title color.
- **Input & Button:** Styles the task input field and add button for a clean look.
- **Task List:** Styles the list items, including completed tasks and delete buttons.
- **Filter Buttons:** Styles the filter buttons with hover effects.
- **Footer:** Centers the footer text and styles it with color.

HERE BELOW THE CSS CODE-----------------------------------------------

body{
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, #92d1cf,#dbb7f3);
}

.container{
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 30px auto;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 5px;
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, #92a8d1,#b7c3f3);
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.header{
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.logo{
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  margin-right: 10px;
}

h1{
  margin: 0;
  color: #fff;
}

.input-container{
  display: flex;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

input[type="text"]{
  flex: 1;
  padding: 10px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 5px 0 0 5px;
}

button{
  padding: 10px 15px;
  border: none;
  background-color: #007BFF;
  columns: #fff;
  border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin-right: 5px;
}

ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
}

li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 10px;
  background-color: #fff;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

.completed {
  background-color: #e1f7d5;
}

.delete-task-btn {
  cursor: pointer;
  color: #d9534f;
  margin-left: 10px;
  font-size: 18px;
}

.task-status {
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  border: 2px solid #ccc;
  border-radius: 4px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-right: 10px;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

.task-status.checked {
  background-color: #28a745;
  border-color: #28a745;
  color: #fff;
}

.task-status.unchecked {
  background-color: #fff;
}

.filter-container {
  margin: 20px 0;
  text-align: center;
}

.filter-container button {
  padding: 5px 10px;
  border: none;
  background-color: #007BFF;
  color: #fff;
  border-radius: 5px;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin: 0 5px;
}

.filter-container button:hover {
  background-color: #0056b3;
}

.footer {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 30px;
  color: #fff;
}

.footer p {
  margin: 5px 0;
}
